{
  "stem": "13063.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Brunnlitz, first of all, the, the factory, the munitions factory, was being built when we, when we came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was schlepping machinery, presses, all kinds of machinery, schlepping, hauling, heaving, yes?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But towards the end, when the machinery was erected and started working-- it was in 1945 already, February-- I was transferred to, to, to painting of artillery shells, so they shouldn't get rusted.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I painted them, with a, with a certain-- with a like a pistol, paint pistol.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was my, my job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who were there?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a few, quite a few people who I knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were, first of all, Feigenbaum, the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] brothers Feigenbaum.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a, a-- on 47th Street in New York a diamond business, a very big diamond business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right now, they have still.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were very-- we were very befriended with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was in Brunnlitz with me, Rosners, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the brothers Rosners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the musicians, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, somebody smuggled an accordion into the Brunnlitz camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think the Czech, the Czech underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a Czech underground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They smuggled a accordion [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] into the camp, into the Brunnlitz camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of the Rosners played, when the Russian-- the final Russian offensive started, on January 12, 1945.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the final offensive that brought the Russians into, into Berlin, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] into outskirts of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he, he played, as a sign of happiness, a sign of hope that salvation is coming, that liberation is coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Poldek-- Pfefferberg, His name was Pfefferberg, now it's Page.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He was a man of great stature and brilliance.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
